{
  "bio": "Zach Miller is an artist based in Oklahoma City working primarily in painting, drawing, printmaking, and new media.",
  "artist_statement": [
    "The studio is a place of perpetual becoming, never arriving.",
    "In the studio, I create gaps between meaning and form, presence and absence, order and entropy. The gaps inhale and exhale. They ask not what reality is, but what it feels like to reach toward something that can never be fully held."
